Dovecot is an open source IMAP and POP3 email server
 Dovecot is an open source IMAP and POP3 email server for UNIX-like systems, written with security primarily in mind.
 
 The Packages is created for Apple TV 2 devices. 
 It is not recommended to install a mail server on an iPhone, an iPad or an iPod.
 
 Instead of Fetchmail you can use 'mpop'.
